Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch break, I chase after
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your laughing voice, to the library
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shadow flutters on the curtain
